* Courvoisier Gold (US Only)
* Courvoisier Rose (US Only)

==Accolades==
Courvoisier was granted the &#x27;Prestige de la France&#x27; in 1984 for providing quality products in France and remains the only cognac house to have received the award. Liquor ratings aggregator Proof66 lists the Courvoisier 21 among the Top 20 rated brandies/cognacs in the world.

